hh3cSlbg.name: hh3cSlbg

revisions.description: The initial revision of this MIB module.

hh3cSlbg.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip: 100085

hh3cSlbgGroupTable.name: hh3cSlbgGroupTable
hh3cSlbgGroupTable.description: A table of service loopback group objects.

hh3cSlbgGroupNumber.name: hh3cSlbgGroupNumber
hh3cSlbgGroupNumber.description: Serial number of the service loopback group.

hh3cSlbgGroupSrvType.name: hh3cSlbgGroupSrvType
hh3cSlbgGroupSrvType.description: Service type of the service loopback group. ipv6: IPv6 unicast service type. ipv6mc: IPv6 multicast service type. tunnel: Unicast tunnel service type. multicastTunnel: Multicast tunnel service type. mpls: MPLS service type.

hh3cSlbgGroupRowStatus.name: hh3cSlbgGroupRowStatus
hh3cSlbgGroupRowStatus.description: This object is used to create, modify, or delete rows. hh3cSlbgGroupNumber and hh3cSlbgGroupSrvType must have a valid value before a row can be activated.

hh3cSlbgPortEntry.name: hh3cSlbgPortEntry
hh3cSlbgPortEntry.description: The service loopback group port entry.

hh3cSlbgPortIndex.name: hh3cSlbgPortIndex
hh3cSlbgPortIndex.description: Interface index of the port, which is defined in RFC1213 (MIB-II).

hh3cSlbgPortAttachedGroupNumber.name: hh3cSlbgPortAttachedGroupNumber
hh3cSlbgPortAttachedGroupNumber.description: The value of the service group number to which this port is assigned. The value is zero if the port is not assigned to any service loopback group.

hh3cSlbgPortSelectedGroupNumber.name: hh3cSlbgPortSelectedGroupNumber
hh3cSlbgPortSelectedGroupNumber.description: The value of the service group number to which this selected port is assigned. The value is zero if the port is not selected or not assigned to any service loopback group.
